{"tid":781210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"離岸人民幣再急挫　逼近6.96元關口","createTime":"2018-08-15T17:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T12:13:50.000Z","uid":147314,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3faf1dc77b8ae65ca97ca12081aaba289279a3cb","tid":781210,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1918268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1918268%2F&d=IXDrlsmRLPkPJUEFbulJzxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=954c3503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1918268/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日 00:13 <br />\n<br />\n離岸人民幣曾挫589點子 逼近6.96元關口<br />\n<br />\n離岸人民幣兌美元(CNH)在周三美國紐約交易時段急挫超過500點子，最低曾觸及6.9584元，逼近6.96關口。<br />\n<br />\n截至本港凌晨零時8分，CNH跌0.77%或者532點子，報6.9527元；盤中低位曾見6.9584，跌幅達589點子。<br />\n<br />\n在岸人民幣兌美元（CNY）同樣急挫，本港周三晚上11時30分，CNY收報6.9350元，較周二夜市收盤下跌514點子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/08/16/1918268_ac85c096dd58481701478261c9369c61_320.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F1918268_ac85c096dd58481701478261c9369c61_320.png&h=26b54759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現報6.9472 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e4a17f2cf3c74c879b73422930bfbcc17bf3ae","tid":781210,"uid":54876,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3faf1dc77b8ae65ca97ca12081aaba289279a3cb","tid":781210,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1918268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1918268%2F&d=IXDrlsmRLPkPJUEFbulJzxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=954c3503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1918268